negative.review:
Welp I wrote a couple of paragraphs and accidentally closed Steam. So the TLDR;

The main villain does not care if you take out his key people, NPCs are brainless, game is buggy at times, and I beat the whole game with my first gun (MS16). Slap a suppressor and armor piercing rounds on it and you're good to go.

Compared to Far Cry 3 and 4, this game is trash.

